name: R E V O L U T I O N

metadata.name: Aina | Genesis
metadata.description:
"Hi I'm Aina from the libertarians.
You will witness terrible days.
They've come to take away our freedom and nature.
They were stronger than us and they were ruthless.
We've had losses, and we resisted them.
They tried to take our lives away from us.
There were things they forgot

Our Soul,
Our World, 
Our Dream."
